;d pay per year to lease the Subaru Legacy is:&nbsp;<\/span><\/span>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"SL","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"If gas is free, the maximum I'd pay per year to lease the Subaru Legacy is:\u00a0","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"ContentType","ContentType":"ValidNumber","ValidDateType":"DateWithFormat","ValidPhoneType":"ValidUSPhone","ValidZipType":"ValidUSZip"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"SearchSource":{"AllowFreeResponse":"false"},"QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnload(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place Your Javascript Below This Line*\/\n\njQuery(\"#\"+this.questionId+\" .InputText\").css(\"width\", \"150px\");\n\t\nvar inputs = $(this.getQuestionContainer()).select('input[type=\"text\"]');\n\nfor (var i = 0; i < inputs.length; i++) {\n  var input = inputs[i];\n  $(input).insert({before: '$ '});\n  $(input).insert({after: ' per year'});\n\n}\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnPageSubmit(function()\n{\n\tvar subaru_enjoy_js = document.getElementById('QR~' + this.questionId).value;\n\tsubaru_enjoy_js = parseFloat(subaru_enjoy_js.replace(\/,\/g, ''));\n\tQualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('subaru_enjoy_js', subaru_enjoy_js);\n});","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"QuestionText_Unsafe":"This rating means that if gas is free, the maximum I'd pay per year to lease the Subaru Legacy is:&nbsp;","DataExportTag":"subaru_enjoy2","QuestionID":"QID590"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_bmebs5HpMXjiq3A","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID404","SecondaryAttribute":"Now we\u2019d like to ask you to choose between pairs of cars at many different annual lease payments..","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Now we&rsquo;d like to ask you to choose between pairs of cars at many different annual lease payments.&nbsp;To do this, we&#39;ll use something called a choice table.<\/span><br \/>\n&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Here&#39;s how it works. The table below has 31 rows. In <strong>each row<\/strong>, we&#39;d like you to select whether you prefer to lease the Dodge Charger or the Ford Fusion.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The Ford Fusion costs the same in each row: $2000 per year.<\/span><\/li>\n\t<li><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The Dodge Charger costs a different amount in each row, ranging from $500 to $3500.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<p><br \/>\n<span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The price of the Charger is relatively low at the top and relatively high at the bottom. Thus, many (although not all) people will choose the Charger at the top and the Fusion at the bottom. The main thing to decide is where you want to switch from the Charger to the Fusion.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">To help you answer quickly, we programmed the computer to select on the left for all rows above where you click, and on the right for all rows below. So you just need to decide where you want to switch from left to right, and click there. You can click as many times as you want. Then click &quot;Next&quot; when you are happy with your final choices.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nPlease make your choices in the table below. This one is just practice.<\/span><\/p>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"practice_mpl","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Now we\u2019d like to ask you to choose between pairs of cars at many different annual lease payments....","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID404","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"QuestionJS":false}},{"SurveyID":"SV_bmebs5HpMXjiq3A","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID632","SecondaryAttribute":"Please click on the choice you would prefer given the annual lease prices below","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<span style=\"color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">Please click on the choice you would prefer given the annual lease prices below<\/span>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"nissan_ford_cost_r","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAHR","SubSelector":"TX","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","LabelPosition":"BELOW"},"QuestionDescription":"Please click on the choice you would prefer given the annual lease prices below","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Nissan Altima for $2000"},"2":{"Display":"Ford Fusion for $2000"}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID632","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnPageSubmit(function()\n{\n\tvar selectedRecode = this.getChoiceRecodeValue(this.getSelectedChoices());\n\tif (selectedRecode == 1) {  \/\/ selected dynamic value on the left\n\t\tvar prev_sign = 1;\n\t} else {  \/\/ selected fixed 2000 value on the right\n\t\tvar prev_sign = -1;\n\t}\n\tQualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('prev_sign', parseInt(prev_sign));\n\tvar left_car = 2000;\n\tQualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('left_car', parseInt(left_car));\n});"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_bmebs5HpMXjiq3A","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID673","SecondaryAttribute":"Please click on the choice you would prefer given the annual lease prices below","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<span style=\"color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">Please click on the choice you would prefer given the annual lease prices below<\/span>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAHR","SubSelector":"TX","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","LabelPosition":"BELOW"},"QuestionDescription":"Please click on the choice you would prefer given the annual lease prices below","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Nissan Altima for $$e{${e:\/\/Field\/left_car_value} + ${e:\/\/Field\/prev_sign} * (800 * 0.5^(${lm:\/\/CurrentLoopNumber}-1))}"},"2":{"Display":"Ford Fusion for $2000"}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnPageSubmit(function()\n{\n\tvar selectedRecode = this.getChoiceRecodeValue(this.getSelectedChoices());\n\tif (selectedRecode == 1) {  \/\/ selected dynamic value on the left\n\t\tvar sign = 1;\n\t} else {  \/\/ selected fixed 2000 value on the right\n\t\tvar sign = -1;\n\t}\n\t\n\tvar prev_sign = parseInt(\"${e:\/\/Field\/prev_sign}\");\n\tvar prev_left_car_value = parseInt(\"${e:\/\/Field\/left_car_value}\");\n\tvar current_loop_num = parseInt(\"${lm:\/\/CurrentLoopNumber}\");\n\tvar left_car_value = prev_left_car_value + prev_sign * (800 * Math.pow(0.5, (current_loop_num - 1)));\n\t\n\tQualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('left_car_value', left_car_value);  \/\/ this is \"previous\" from PoV of \"tomorrow\"\n\tQualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('prev_sign', parseInt(sign));  \/\/ save this for \"tomorrow\"\n\t\/\/ alert(prev_left_car_value + ',' + current_loop_num + ',' + left_car_value);\n\t\n\t\/\/ save out WTP value if this is the 5th row\n\tif (current_loop_num == 4) {\n\t\tif (selectedRecode == 1) {  \/\/ selected left on 5th screen\n\t\t\tQualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('nissan_lease_wtp_e', left_car_value + 50);\n\t\t\tQualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('ford_lease_wtp_e_nissan', 2000);\n\t\t} else {  \/\/ selected 2000 value on 5th screen\n\t\t\tQualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('nissan_lease_wtp_e', left_car_value - 50);\n\t\t\tQualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('ford_lease_wtp_e_nissan', 2000);\n\t\t}\n\t\t\n\t\t\/\/ reset the left_car_value to $2000 for the next MPL\n\t\tQualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('left_car_value', 2000);\n\t\t\n\t\t\/\/ reset prev_sign to be 1 for the next MPL\n\t\tQualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('prev_sign', 1);\n\t}\n});","QuestionText_Unsafe":"<span style=\"color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">Please click on the choice you would prefer given the annual lease prices below<\/span>","DataExportTag":"nissan_ford_cost_ri","QuestionID":"QID673"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_bmebs5HpMXjiq3A","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID630","SecondaryAttribute":"Please click on the choice you would prefer given the annual lease prices below.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please click on the choice you would prefer given the annual lease prices below.","QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnPageSubmit(function()\n{\n\tvar selectedRecode = this.getChoiceRecodeValue(this.getSelectedChoices());\n\tif (selectedRecode == 4) {  \/\/ selected