pan><\/p>\n&nbsp;\n\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-6dfd5734-7fff-3075-d1ff-f94caf4cddbd\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">For the entire survey, imagine the following scenario:<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-6dfd5734-7fff-3075-d1ff-f94caf4cddbd\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Your primary car broke down and can't be used anymore.<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n\t<li><span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">To replace your primary car, you will lease a car for the next 3 years.<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n\t<li><span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Any dealership would offer you the same lease contract, so there\u2019s no need to shop around. <\/span><\/span><\/li>\n\t<li><span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">You (and anyone else in your household) would drive this car the amount that you told us earlier<\/span><\/span><span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: ${e:\/\/Field\/miles_driven_2019} miles per year. <\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"We\u2019d like to learn how consumers choose what car to lease in the current economic environment.\u00a0 \u00a0...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-6dfd5734-7fff-3075-d1ff-f94caf4cddbd\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">We&rsquo;d like to learn how consumers choose what car to lease in the current economic environment.&nbsp;<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n&nbsp;\n\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-6dfd5734-7fff-3075-d1ff-f94caf4cddbd\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">For the entire survey, imagine the following scenario:<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-6dfd5734-7fff-3075-d1ff-f94caf4cddbd\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Your primary car broke down and can&#39;t be used anymore.<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">To replace your primary car, you will lease a car for the next 3 years.<\/span><\/span>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Any dealership would offer you the same lease contract, so there&rsquo;s no need to shop around. <\/span><\/span><\/li>\n\t<li><span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">You (and anyone else in your household) would drive this car the amount that you told us earlier<\/span><\/span><span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: ${q:\/\/QID388\/ChoiceTextEntryValue} miles per year. <\/span><\/span><\/li>\n\t<li><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The average gas price for the next three years will be the same as what you told us you paid in 2019: $${e:\/\/Field\/gas_price_estimate} per gallon.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"DataExportTag":"description_scenario","QuestionID":"QID488","QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnload(function()\n{\n\t\/\/ compute the annual gas costs \n\t\n\tvar miles_driven_2019 = \"${e:\/\/Field\/miles_driven_2019}\";\n\tvar gas_price_estimate = parseFloat(\"${e:\/\/Field\/gas_price_estimate}\");\n\t\n\t\t\/\/ for 30 MPG\n\tvar gas_cost_thirty = miles_driven_2019 \/ 30.0 * gas_price_estimate;\t\n\tQualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData(\"gas_cost_thirty\", gas_cost_thirty);\n\t\n\t\t\/\/ for 23 MPG\n\tvar gas_cost_twentythree = miles_driven_2019 \/ 23.0 * gas_price_estimate;\n\tQualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData(\"gas_cost_twentythree\", gas_cost_twentythree);\n\n});"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_bmebs5HpMXjiq3A","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID487","SecondaryAttribute":"We\u2019d like to learn how much you would like to have each of the 4 cars on the next 4 screens, sett.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">We&rsquo;d like to learn how much you would like to have each of the 4 cars on the next 4 screens, setting aside gas costs. In order to tell us that, please <strong>imagine for the next 4 screens that gas is free <\/strong>and that you&#39;d still drive the <\/span><span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">${e:\/\/Field\/miles_driven_2019} miles per year you told us earlier<\/span><\/span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">. <\/span><br \/>\n<br \/>\n<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-6dfd5734-7fff-3075-d1ff-f94caf4cddbd\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">For each car on the next 4 screens, we&#39;ll ask you to tell us<\/span><\/span><span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> the maximum amount of money you&#39;d be willing to pay <\/span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">per year<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> <\/span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">to lease each of the cars, <strong>if gas is free<\/strong>.<\/span><\/span>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"descrip_enjoy1","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"We\u2019d like to learn how much you would like to have each of the 4 cars on the next 4 screens, sett...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID487","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_bmebs5HpMXjiq3A","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID588","SecondaryAttribute":"We\u2019d like to learn how much you would like to have each of the 4 cars on the next 4 screens, sett.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">We&rsquo;d like to learn how much you would like to have each of the 4 cars on the next 4 screens, setting aside gas costs. In order to tell us that, please <strong>imagine for the next 4 s