ey you&#39;d be willing to pay <\/span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">per year<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> <\/span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">to lease each of the 4 cars below, <strong>if gas is free<\/strong>.<\/span><\/span>\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<div>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:1160px;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 290px;\">\n\t\t\t<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2020 Subaru Legacy<br \/>\n\t\t\t<br \/>\n\t\t\t<img src=\"https:\/\/nyu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/Graphic.php?IM=IM_emPnqYibw0iqXSl\" style=\"width: 350px; height: 171px;\" \/><\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 290px;\">&nbsp;\n\t\t\t<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2020 Nissan&nbsp;Altima<\/div>\n\t\t\t<img src=\"https:\/\/nyu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/Graphic.php?IM=IM_byd3f9eORLE2TWJ\" \/><br \/>\n\t\t\t<br \/>\n\t\t\t&nbsp;<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 290px;\">2020 Ford Fusion<br \/>\n\t\t\t<br \/>\n\t\t\t<img height=\"152\" src=\"https:\/\/nyu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/Graphic.php?IM=IM_9mqvd3ZWueCqQIt\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 152px;\" width=\"300\" \/><\/td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 290px;\">\n\t\t\t<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2020 Honda Accord<\/div>\n\t\t\t<br \/>\n\t\t\t<img src=\"https:\/\/nyu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/Graphic.php?IM=IM_cYHsA5pBrsTDpiJ\" \/><\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: left;\">Key attributes:\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Horsepower: 182 hp<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>MPG: 30&nbsp;(combined city\/highway)<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Engine: 2.5&nbsp;L 4-cylinder<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Transmission: CVT<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Total seats: 5<\/li>\n\t\t\t<\/ul>\n\t\t\tPlease click <a href=\"https:\/\/www.subaru.com\/vehicles\/legacy\/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a> for more information.&nbsp;<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>Key attributes:\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Horsepower: 182 hp<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>MPG: 30&nbsp;(combined city\/highway)<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Engine: 2.5 L 4-cylinder<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Transmission: CVT<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Total seats: 5<\/li>\n\t\t\t<\/ul>\n\t\t\tPlease click&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.nissanusa.com\/vehicles\/cars\/altima.html\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a>&nbsp;for more information.&nbsp;<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>Key attributes:\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Horsepower: 175&nbsp;hp<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>MPG: 23&nbsp;(combined city\/highway)<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Engine: 2.0&nbsp;L 4-cylinder<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Transmission: Automatic<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Total seats: 5<\/li>\n\t\t\t<\/ul>\n\t\t\tPlease click <a href=\"https:\/\/www.ford.com\/cars\/fusion\/\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a> for more information.&nbsp;<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>Key attributes:\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Horsepower: 192 hp<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>MPG: 30&nbsp;(combined city\/highway)<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Engine: 1.5 L 4-cylinder<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Transmission: 6-speed manual<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Total seats: 5<\/li>\n\t\t\t<\/ul>\n\t\t\tPlease click&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/automobiles.honda.com\/accord-sedan\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a>&nbsp;for more information.&nbsp;<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>","DataExportTag":"descrip_enjoy2","QuestionID":"QID588"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_bmebs5HpMXjiq3A","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID480","SecondaryAttribute":"We\u2019d like to make the rest of your choices as real as possible, so your participation bonus will..","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<p><span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">We&rsquo;d like to make the rest of your choices as real as possible, so your participation bonus will depend on the actual value that you would get from a choice in reality. <strong>The bottom line is that it is in your best interest to carefully and honestly tell us which car you&#39;d prefer at the price we state!<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\nSpecifically, we&#39;ll take one choice you make based on the upcoming screens and pay you your <strong>rescaled net annual value<\/strong>&nbsp;from the car you chose. Your <strong>net annual value<\/strong><strong> <\/strong>from a car equals:<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-03a8901a-7fff-531c-8da6-51f6c4a310f3\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">the maximum you told us earlier that you&#39;d pay per year to lease the car if gas is free,&nbsp;<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n\t<li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-03a8901a-7fff-531c-8da6-51f6c4a310f3\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">minus the yearly gas cost. We&rsquo;ll calculate that with the car&rsquo;s official miles-per-gallon rating as well as the amount you drove in 2019 and the average gas price you paid in 2019, both of which you told us earlier,<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n\t<li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-03a8901a-7fff-531c-8da6-51f6c4a310f3\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">minus the yearly lease payment we quote on the following screens.<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<font face=\"Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">We will then <strong>rescale<\/strong>&nbsp;your <strong>net annual value<\/strong>&nbsp;so that the minimum bonus you could possibly earn (across all choices you make based on the upcoming screens) is 1,000 AmeriPoints ($1 cash equivalent), and the maximum bonus you could possibly earn is 10,000 AmeriPoints ($10 cash equivalent).<br \/>\nClick <a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/file\/d\/16A0nyzcgN4UDinaXxCGG9e0Y3Y2mTiCl\/view?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a> for more information.<\/span><\/font>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"payment_intro_screen","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"We\u2019d like to make the rest of your choices as real as possible, so your participation bonus will...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID480","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_bmebs5HpMXjiq3A","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID389","SecondaryAttribute":"What do you think was the average price you paid per gallon\u00a0for gas in 2019? (For reference, the...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\">What do you think was the average price you paid <strong>per gallon&nbsp;<\/strong>for gas in 2019? (For reference, the average gas price in your state in 2019 was ${e:\/\/Field\/avg_price_last_yr}.)<\/span><\/span>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"SL","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"What do you think was the average price you paid per gallon\u00a0for gas in 2019? (For reference, the...","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"ContentType","ContentType":"ValidNumber","ValidDateType":"DateWithFormat","ValidPhoneType":"ValidUSPhone","ValidZipType":"ValidUSZip"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"SearchSource":{"AllowFreeResponse":"false"},"QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnload(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place Your Javascript Below This Line*\/\n\njQuery(\"#\"+this.questionId+\" .InputText\").css(\"width\", \"150px\");\n\n\t\nvar inputs = $(this.getQuestionContainer()).select('input[type=\"text\"]');\n\nfor (var i = 0; i < inputs.length; i++) {\n  var input = inputs[i];\n  $(input).insert({before: '$ '});\n  $(input).insert({after: ' per gallon'});\n}\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnPageSubmit(function()\n{\n\tvar gas_price_estimate = document.getElementById('QR~' + this.questionId).value;\n\tgas_price_estimate = parseFloat(gas_price_estimate);\n\tQualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('gas_price_estimate', gas_price_estimate.toFixed(2));\n});","QuestionText_Unsafe":"What do you think will be the average gas price in your area over the next 3 years?","DataExportTag":"gas_price","QuestionID":"QID389","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_bmebs5HpMXjiq3A","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID597","SecondaryAttribute":"You can take this survey on your phone if needed, but it will be much easier to read if you take...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 22px;\">You can take this survey on your phone if needed, but it will be much easier to read if you take it on a computer or tablet.<\/span><\/font><\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:22px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans