s that you told us earlier.<\/span>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"You have finished two of the four car comparisons! For these final two car comparisons, we'll add...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<span style=\"color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">You have finished two of the four choice tables!&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\nFor these final two, we'll add labels to the cars' pictures. These labels are part of the labels that must be posted on car windows at dealerships. They report averages for each car at typical usage patterns.<\/span>","DataExportTag":"endline_intro_costp","QuestionID":"QID539"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_bmebs5HpMXjiq3A","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID540","SecondaryAttribute":"You have finished two of the four car comparisons!\u00a0 For these final two car comparisons, we\u2019ll ad","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">You have finished two of the four car comparisons!&nbsp;<br \/>\n<br \/>\nFor these final two car comparisons, we&rsquo;ll add SmartWay Vehicle labels to some cars. Cars that meet SmartWay Vehicle standards for fuel economy and environmental performance will have SmartWay Vehicle labels. Cars that do not meet these standards will not have SmartWay Vehicle labels.<\/span>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"You have finished two of the four car comparisons!\u00a0 For these final two car comparisons, we\u2019ll ad...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}